sentences.english: Unhappy unhappier unhappiest Anyway I'm uneasier than you about the coming physics test .
sentences.chinese: 反正我比你對即將到來的物理考試更擔心。

sentences.english: Well, anyhow, I rang the bell.
sentences.chinese: 好吧，不管好歹，反正我按鈴了。

sentences.english: I expected it to be a cakewalk anyway.
sentences.chinese: 我期望這是一個步態競賽反正。

sentences.english: Pretty easy for the background as only a few picks there.
sentences.chinese: 背景的選擇自不必說了，反正就那麼幾個。

sentences.english: Not far fetched to say you love me, anyway, my soul has patches of litter.
sentences.chinese: 你也不必牽強再說愛我，反正我的靈魂已片片凋落。

sentences.english: I didn’t have to become a literary giant.
sentences.chinese: 反正我從來沒有想過要成爲大文豪。

sentences.english: My sisters may write to me. They will have nothing else to do.
sentences.chinese: 姐妹們倒可以常常寫信給我，反正她們無事可做。

sentences.english: And there were already a half-dozen Elizabeth Taylors here anyway.
sentences.chinese: 而且反正酒吧裏早已有六名伊麗莎白泰勒了。

sentences.english: Oh, I don't fly so much anyway, so I don't really worry.
sentences.chinese: 哦，我反正不常飛，所以也不怎麼擔心。

sentences.english: The rooms were cleaned and wallpapered.
sentences.chinese: 反正我們也打算給那個房間貼牆紙的。

sentences.english: Anyways, I hope you get this man, hit me back.
sentences.chinese: 反正，我相當期望您能瞅見這封信，給我歸信吧。

sentences.english: They will all be forgotten in fifty years anyway.
sentences.chinese: 反正五十年內他們將通通被遺忘。
